---
import BorderBoxComponent from "../components/BorderBoxComponent.astro"
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
---
<BaseLayout PageTitle = "🫣 找不到页面">
    <main class="container mx-auto p-8 pt-16 space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black">404</h1>
        <p class="font-light">您访问了一个不存在的页面，请检查链接是否正确，如果你确定链接正确是网站的错误，请给我发邮件<span class="text-sm underline">（标题注明：[页面错误] 等）</span> 谢谢。</p>
        <a class="inline-block font-light text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="/">返回首页</a>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>